column1: Weighted MRI size (256, 256, 1) in T2, exposing the head of a man of 37 years old, of coronal section n°107 starting from the back of the skull. The section reveals the white matter of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 527.3438 mm³, the cortex of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 2129.1504 mm³, the white matter of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 622.2656 mm³ and the cortex of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 2366.4551 mm³.
